<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 00:38:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列内阁秘书告诉AG：你们的工作程序有缺陷，而不是内塔尼亚胡的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-cabinet-secretary-tells-ag-your-work-procedures-are-flawed-not-netanyahus/00000191-42e8-d8bb-a5df-fff9178a0000</link><description>以色列总检察长告诉内塔尼亚胡，他的内阁工作程序存在缺陷，损害了公共利益——对国家安全造成严重影响——之后，内阁秘书指控总检察长超越了她的职权</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 20:05:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-cabinet-secretary-tells-ag-your-work-procedures-are-flawed-not-netanyahus/00000191-42e8-d8bb-a5df-fff9178a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部长敦促政府恢复司法改革</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-minister-urges-government-to-resume-judicial-overhaul/00000191-4262-dcbf-a3bb-e7ff61820000</link><description>在几位联盟议员呼吁罢免总检察长后，以色列司法部长亚里夫·莱文敦促他们与他一起努力重启司法改革，特别是通过一项法律，让政府对法官的选择有更多的控制权</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 17:51:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-minister-urges-government-to-resume-judicial-overhaul/00000191-4262-dcbf-a3bb-e7ff61820000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡还是人质？美国犹太人是时候做出选择了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-11/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahu-or-the-hostages-its-time-for-u-s-jews-to-choose/00000191-4207-debc-a793-4eaf49200000</link><description>每个关心以色列和人质的人都必须做出决定，他们是与被哈马斯扣押的人质家属站在一起，还是与失败的政客站在一起，我们永远不应该忘记，在这场暴行发生时，他们仍在掌权。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 17:22:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-11/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahu-or-the-hostages-its-time-for-u-s-jews-to-choose/00000191-4207-debc-a793-4eaf49200000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在约旦河西岸驾车枪击事件中丧生，一人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-killed-one-wounded-in-drive-by-shooting-attack-in-west-bank/00000191-41fa-d8bb-a5df-fffbcc3e0000</link><description>以色列军方认为，袭击者在西岸北部的90号公路上向一辆车开枪，随后继续行驶，并向第二辆车开枪。救援部门宣布一名受害者当场死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 17:08:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-killed-one-wounded-in-drive-by-shooting-attack-in-west-bank/00000191-41fa-d8bb-a5df-fffbcc3e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 310 天：据报道，官员要求真主党推迟对以色列袭击的答复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-310-officials-reportedly-ask-hezbollah-to-delay-reply-to-israel-strike/00000191-4234-d8bb-a5df-ffb520160000</link><description>以色列消息人士告诉《国土报》，以色列有迹象表明哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔希望达成停火/释放人质协议，并补充说“问题是内塔尼亚胡是否愿意” ■ 以色列男子在约旦河西岸枪击事件中丧生 ■ 以色列政府采纳阻止协议访问真主党附属新闻频道 Al-Mayadeen ■ 这是战争进入 310 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 16:24:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-310-officials-reportedly-ask-hezbollah-to-delay-reply-to-israel-strike/00000191-4234-d8bb-a5df-ffb520160000</guid></item><item><title>如果加沙人质谈判失败，美国和其他调解人威胁称以色列和哈马斯将出面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-and-other-mediators-threaten-to-call-out-israel-hamas-if-gaza-hostage-talks-fail/00000191-415c-d283-ad9f-e1fe88090000</link><description>一位外交消息人士告诉《国土报》，拜登政府——迄今为止一直将谈判陷入僵局归咎于哈马斯——已经到了这样的地步：内塔尼亚胡总理的行为将导致美国公开指责他破坏谈判并阻止人质获释。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 16:20:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-and-other-mediators-threaten-to-call-out-israel-hamas-if-gaza-hostage-talks-fail/00000191-415c-d283-ad9f-e1fe88090000</guid></item><item><title>新研究揭示了加沙地带被释放的以色列母亲和儿童的精神和身体创伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/new-study-reveals-mental-physical-traumas-of-israelis-freed-from-captivity-in-gaza/00000191-41fc-d8bb-a5df-fffdbc420000</link><description>这项新研究基于 11 月与哈马斯达成人质协议后返回以色列的 19 名青年和 7 名妇女所接受的治疗，揭示了在加沙被囚禁 50 天的影响，以及大多数人目睹谋杀或绑架的最初袭击家庭成员的</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 16:14:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/new-study-reveals-mental-physical-traumas-of-israelis-freed-from-captivity-in-gaza/00000191-41fc-d8bb-a5df-fffdbc420000</guid></item><item><title>以色列以国家安全为由封锁真主党附属新闻频道 Al Mayadeen</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/israel-blocks-hezbollah-affiliated-news-channel-al-mayadeen-citing-national-security/00000191-41da-d2c9-af99-67fb323c0000</link><description>这项立法由议会于 4 月 1 日通过，政府于 5 月一致通过，授权通讯部长下令外国频道停止广播 45 天。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 15:29:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/israel-blocks-hezbollah-affiliated-news-channel-al-mayadeen-citing-national-security/00000191-41da-d2c9-af99-67fb323c0000</guid></item><item><title>右翼抗议者袭击以色列国防军高级律师的家，抗议巴勒斯坦被拘留者的虐待行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/right-wingers-descend-on-top-idf-lawyers-home-over-probe-of-palestinian-detainees-abuse/00000191-419b-d2c9-af99-67bbf62d0000</link><description>以色列军事倡导者伊法特·托梅尔·耶鲁沙尔米 (Yifat Tomer-Yerushalmi) 将军在长期阴谋论中成为右翼最新的恶魔，该阴谋论声称左翼正在利用司法越权来控制国家，目前她正在起诉涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦被拘留者的以色列国防军士兵。斯德泰曼拘留中心</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 15:22:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/right-wingers-descend-on-top-idf-lawyers-home-over-probe-of-palestinian-detainees-abuse/00000191-419b-d2c9-af99-67bbf62d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军法院将五名涉嫌虐待斯德泰曼巴勒斯坦被拘留者的士兵的逮捕期限延长三天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-prosecution-extends-arrest-of-5-soldiers-suspected-of-abusing-palestinian-detainee/00000191-41d7-dcbf-a3bb-e5dfda400000</link><description>军事法庭法官裁定将以色列国防军预备役人员的逮捕期限延长三天，称收集到的证据否定了他们辩护小组提供的医学解释。检方表示，不反对在可能将嫌疑人软禁之前对他们的拘留进行审查</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 15:19:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-prosecution-extends-arrest-of-5-soldiers-suspected-of-abusing-palestinian-detainee/00000191-41d7-dcbf-a3bb-e5dfda400000</guid></item><item><title>AG：以色列无法资助为以色列国防军服役的极端正统派男子的孩子提供日托服务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/ag-israel-cannot-finance-daycare-for-ultra-orthodox-slated-for-idf-service/00000191-4190-d505-a39b-d9b42d830000</link><description>据以色列总检察长称，由于高等法院裁定不准极端正统派男子服兵役，因此国家不能再为因应征加入以色列国防军的犹太学院学生的孩子提供日托费用</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 15:11:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/ag-israel-cannot-finance-daycare-for-ultra-orthodox-slated-for-idf-service/00000191-4190-d505-a39b-d9b42d830000</guid></item><item><title>以色列节目报道了被绑架到加沙的被释放的人质兄弟姐妹，以争夺艾美奖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-show-up-for-emmy-for-covering-freed-hostage-siblings-kidnapped-into-gaza/00000191-41a6-d2c9-af99-67a79a7c0000</link><description>以色列调查新闻电视节目《Uvda》因题为“被囚禁的兄弟姐妹”的片段获得提名，该片段对获释人质 Itay 和 Maya Regev 进行了深入采访，他们参加了 Nova 节日，并于 10 月 7 日被哈马斯劫持为人质</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 14:24:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-show-up-for-emmy-for-covering-freed-hostage-siblings-kidnapped-into-gaza/00000191-41a6-d2c9-af99-67a79a7c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列科学家发现果蝠具有精神时间旅行能力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-08-11/ty-article/fruit-bats-are-capable-of-mental-time-travel-israeli-scientists-discover/00000191-4141-d1fa-ad9d-67d716e10000</link><description>约西·约维尔和团队发现，特拉维夫的埃及果蝠根据情景记忆提前计划外出觅食</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 12:52:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-08-11/ty-article/fruit-bats-are-capable-of-mental-time-travel-israeli-scientists-discover/00000191-4141-d1fa-ad9d-67d716e10000</guid></item><item><title>“我们不能妥协”：极右翼 MK 为定居者袭击阿拉伯-以色列妇女辩护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/we-cant-compromise-israeli-far-right-mk-defends-settler-attack-on-arab-israeli-women/00000191-40f8-d2a2-a7b1-4ffb354f0000</link><description>本-格维尔党的议员桑·哈-梅莱赫 (MK Son Har-Melech) 为犹太袭击者辩护，声称车内“没有以色列车牌”的受袭击阿拉伯妇女可能是针对西岸定居者的间谍</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 11:28:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/we-cant-compromise-israeli-far-right-mk-defends-settler-attack-on-arab-israeli-women/00000191-40f8-d2a2-a7b1-4ffb354f0000</guid></item><item><title>奥运冠军展示了以色列体育心态的另一面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/london-2012/olympics-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/with-hard-work-and-discipline-our-olympic-winners-prove-israelis-can-excel-in-sports/00000191-40e9-d927-a9b5-c1f9cb2a0000</link><description>我们倾向于认为，典型的以色列心态不适合从年轻时就开始严格的训练和营养制度以及艰苦的工作。随后以色列艺术体操队获得银牌</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 10:53:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/london-2012/olympics-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/with-hard-work-and-discipline-our-olympic-winners-prove-israelis-can-excel-in-sports/00000191-40e9-d927-a9b5-c1f9cb2a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高级陆军律师在以色列议会小组就涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦囚犯一案作证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/top-idf-attorney-testifies-at-knesset-panel-on-suspected-abuse-of-palestinian-prisoner/00000191-404b-d5bd-a59d-605ff59b0000</link><description>许多议员公开批评军法署署长逮捕嫌疑人的方式、调查材料的泄露（包括据称描述这些行为的视频片段）以及军警继续扣押他们的事实</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 10:50:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/top-idf-attorney-testifies-at-knesset-panel-on-suspected-abuse-of-palestinian-prisoner/00000191-404b-d5bd-a59d-605ff59b0000</guid></item><item><title>即使真主党无人机也无法阻止她记录以色列北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/watcher-of-the-skies-of-israels-abandoned-north-creates-art-under-hezbollahs-drones/00000191-32d5-dd83-a9bb-73df570d0000</link><description>在海法艺术博物馆，艺术家哈达尔·赛凡 (Hadar Saifan) 为一个孤独的地区发声。此外，一部纪录片讲述了诺瓦音乐节的悲惨故事，一本新书探讨了战时的女权主义</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 06:33:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/watcher-of-the-skies-of-israels-abandoned-north-creates-art-under-hezbollahs-drones/00000191-32d5-dd83-a9bb-73df570d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列估计伊朗和真主党可能会在周四的停火协议峰会之前发动袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article-live/drone-explodes-in-israels-north-report-arab-envoys-ask-hezbollah-to-delay-retaliation/00000191-3f83-de1f-abd7-3fcb0e790000</link><description>以色列国防军称，约 30 枚火箭弹袭击以色列北部纳哈里亚地区；真主党承担责任 ■ 哈马斯表示已要求调解人提出基于拜登框架的提案 ■ 欧盟外交政策负责人博雷尔呼吁对本格维尔和斯莫特里奇实施制裁，声称他们的言论煽动战争罪</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 03:51:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article-live/drone-explodes-in-israels-north-report-arab-envoys-ask-hezbollah-to-delay-retaliation/00000191-3f83-de1f-abd7-3fcb0e790000</guid></item><item><title>尽管困难重重，美国仍敦促避免以色列与伊朗之间的重大战争并达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/against-the-odds-u-s-presses-to-avoid-major-israel-iran-war-and-seal-hostage-deal/00000191-3d6b-d72d-a3bb-fdeb1b510000</link><description>华盛顿政府非常希望在选举前避免以色列和伊朗之间发生战争，而德黑兰的举动可能符合该政权采取的更广泛的战略步骤</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 03:03:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/against-the-odds-u-s-presses-to-avoid-major-israel-iran-war-and-seal-hostage-deal/00000191-3d6b-d72d-a3bb-fdeb1b510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁投票决定内塔尼亚胡亲自挑选新公务员局长； AG警告此举违法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/defying-ag-netanyahu-seeks-to-install-new-civil-service-commissioner-without-search-panel/00000191-3d6b-d1ef-a1f3-3f7bb0640000</link><description>总检察长在会议前警告部长们，总理对专员的任命是非法的，不应继续进行。该提案获得一致通过</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 03:01:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/defying-ag-netanyahu-seeks-to-install-new-civil-service-commissioner-without-search-panel/00000191-3d6b-d1ef-a1f3-3f7bb0640000</guid></item></channel></rss>